name: Admiral Ozzel (V)
Lore: 'Leader of the Emperor''s Death Squadron assigned to hunt down and crush the Rebellion. As clumsy as he is stupid. Has just failed Darth Vader for the next-to-last time.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting a capital starship at a battleground system, in each battle a player''s first battle destiny draw may not be canceled or reduced and if opponent canceled a just drawn battle destiny, they lose 1 Force.',
